<h2>Edit a Bra</h2>
<p>It is normal to change sizes with certain bras. If you find you need a different size change it here.</p>

<form action='/wishlist/{{id}}?_method=put' method='POST'>
  <input type='text' name='bra[brandName]' value={{brandName}} />
  <input type='text' name='bra[brandStyle]' value={{brandStyle}} />
  <input type='text' name='bra[size]'  value={{size}} />
  <input class='inputSubmit' type='submit' value='Change'/>
</form>

<a href='/wishlist'>Go back to wishlist</a>
